item.title: Urban Sound Processing and Neural Network Model
item.description: Link to github repo Link to kaggle repo Link To Dataset Data exploration The dataset we want to analyze consists of different soundbites each of length 1 second containing the highest intensity in a larger soundbite. The dataset has sounds such as a dog barking, children playing, car horn, and streetmusic. Lets have a look and see how the different kinds of sounds look like in comparison to one another.
